RentersMate – Privacy Policy
Last updated: 8 November 2025

RentersMate is built for UK renters to organise contacts, utilities, documents and insights. We respect your privacy.

Data We Collect
On‑device data only. Properties, meter readings, notices, contacts and templates you use are stored on your device. We do not operate a cloud service and we do not sell personal data.
Analytics/Tracking. The app does not include third‑party analytics or advertising SDKs.
How We Use Information
To provide app features such as council search, email templates and reminders.
Optional links open your email client, phone or browser to contact third parties; we do not receive that data.
Data Sharing
We do not share your personal information with third parties.

Your Choices
You can delete app data at any time by removing the app from your device.
